# Frontend Rules

## Structure

- React functional components + hooks
- Separate game canvas/layer from UI overlay
- Mapbox GL for map; PixiJS or Phaser for game entities (bullets, zombies)

## Mapbox

- Zoom level 18-20 for street visibility
- Use building footprints / boundaries for collision (no walk-through)
- Preload tiles when possible to reduce loading during movement

## Game Loop

- Object pooling for projectiles (bullet hell = many bullets)
- Spatial hash or quadtree for collision detection
- WASD movement, mouse direction for shooting

## State

- Player position: sync with backend on save (5 min or shortcut)
- Local state for real-time movement, no frequent API calls
